---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - HoroTalk">

  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-primary-light to-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light mb-2">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary">Home</a> &rsaquo; Terms of Service
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-light text-sm">Last updated: April 14, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg max-w-none">

      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        By using HoroTalk ("the Service"), you agree to the following terms and conditions. Please read them carefully before using our WhatsApp-based astrology service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">1. Service Description</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        HoroTalk is an AI-powered astrology service accessible via WhatsApp. It provides Vedic astrology readings, birth chart (Kundli) generation, daily Panchang, Kundli matching, Dasha predictions, and related astrological content based on the birth details you provide.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">2. Disclaimer — For Entertainment & Guidance Only</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">
        <strong>Important:</strong> HoroTalk's readings are generated by artificial intelligence and are intended for informational, educational, and entertainment purposes only. They should <strong>not</strong> be treated as:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>Professional medical, legal, or financial advice</li>
        <li>A substitute for consultation with qualified professionals</li>
        <li>Guaranteed predictions of future events</li>
        <li>A replacement for professional astrologers where critical life decisions are concerned</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        You are solely responsible for any decisions you make based on HoroTalk's readings. We are not liable for any outcomes resulting from reliance on our service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">3. Eligibility</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>You must be at least 13 years old to use HoroTalk</li>
        <li>You must have a valid WhatsApp account</li>
        <li>By using the service, you confirm that the birth details you provide are accurate to the best of your knowledge</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">4. Free & Paid Plans</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li><strong>Free plan</strong>: Limited questions per day with basic features. No payment required.</li>
        <li><strong>Paid plans</strong>: Unlock additional features, unlimited questions, and detailed reports. Pricing is listed on our <a href="/pricing" class="text-primary hover:underline">Pricing page</a>.</li>
        <li>All prices are in Indian Rupees (INR) and inclusive of applicable taxes.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">5. Payments & Billing</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>Payments are processed via secure third-party providers (UPI, cards, etc.)</li>
        <li>Subscriptions are billed monthly from the date of purchase</li>
        <li>You can cancel your subscription at any time by messaging us on WhatsApp</li>
        <li>No partial refunds for unused portions of a billing period</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">6. Refund Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We offer a <strong>7-day money-back guarantee</strong> on all paid plans. If you are not satisfied within the first 7 days of your subscription, message us on WhatsApp and we will process a full refund within 7 business days. After the 7-day period, refunds are not available.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">7. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">You agree not to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li>Use the service for any unlawful purpose</li>
        <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, copy, or replicate HoroTalk's AI or algorithms</li>
        <li>Send abusive, threatening, or inappropriate messages</li>
        <li>Resell or redistribute HoroTalk's readings commercially without permission</li>
        <li>Use automated tools or bots to interact with HoroTalk</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        All content generated by HoroTalk, including readings, charts, and reports, is owned by HoroTalk. You may save and share your personal readings for private use but may not commercially redistribute them.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">9. Service Availability</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We strive to keep HoroTalk available 24/7 but do not guarantee uninterrupted service. We may occasionally have downtime for maintenance or updates. We are not liable for any loss due to service interruptions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, HoroTalk and its creators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the service. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount you have paid us in the preceding 12 months.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">11. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in India.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of HoroTalk after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-3">13. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-2">
        If you have questions about these Terms:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-text-light text-sm mb-6">
        <li><strong>WhatsApp</strong>: Message us directly</li>
        <li><strong>Email</strong>: hello@horotalk.in</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
